WEBVTT

00:01:31.625 --> 00:01:33.434
I was born in a democracy,

00:01:33.458 --> 00:01:36.917
in a country called Venezuela,
which is now a dictatorship.

00:01:37.458 --> 00:01:40.708
(Speaks Spanish)

00:01:49.625 --> 00:01:50.893
For 19 years,

00:01:50.917 --> 00:01:53.268
I was the daily cartoonist
for "El Universal,"

00:01:53.292 --> 00:01:55.809
one of the biggest newspapers 
in Venezuela.

00:01:55.833 --> 00:02:00.726
I really enjoyed translating political
and cultural current events into drawings.